  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Harlaw\" title=\"House Harlaw\"><img alt=\"House Harlaw.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a6/House_Harlaw.svg/50px-House_Harlaw.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a6/House_Harlaw.svg/75px-House_Harlaw.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a6/House_Harlaw.svg/100px-House_Harlaw.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> King</span><br />Harron Harlaw</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Harlaw\" title=\"House Harlaw\"><img alt=\"House Harlaw.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a6/House_Harlaw.svg/50px-House_Harlaw.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a6/House_Harlaw.svg/75px-House_Harlaw.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a6/House_Harlaw.svg/100px-House_Harlaw.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Monarch</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Full name</th><td>\nHarron Harlaw</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/High_King_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"High King of the Iron Islands\">High King of the Iron Islands</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Personal Information</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Family</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Dynasty</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Harlaw\" title=\"House Harlaw\">House Harlaw</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Erich_V_Harlaw\" title=\"Erich V Harlaw\">Erich V Harlaw</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">References</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Harron Harlaw</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/High_King_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"High King of the Iron Islands\">High King of the Iron Islands</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Harlaw\" title=\"House Harlaw\">House Harlaw</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Harron_Harlaw&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Harron was chosen at a <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsmoot\" title=\"Kingsmoot\">kingsmoot</a>. He slew <a href=\"/index.php/Gareth_II_Gardener\" title=\"Gareth II Gardener\">Gareth II Gardener</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Reach\" title=\"King of the Reach\">King of the Reach</a>, beneath the walls of <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_driftwood_crowns.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_driftwood_crowns.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\